node.text:
Can the GOAT make a Lenzerheide comeback? 🐐 

2017 saw @gregminnaar put down a blinder of a run to hold onto the leaders jersey during round 5 of the season. A dramatic ongoing battle with @aarongwin1 that came to a head in Val Di Sole.

As the tables turn, can Minnaar go for gold again this weekend? 🥇 

Tune into Red Bull TV this Saturday to find out. 📺 

#uci #mtb #dh #downhill #lenzerheide

Another day on the hill. ✅

Lenzerheide delivered the goods as the 4th round of the @uci_mountainbike Downhill World Cup came to a head this weekend in the high-alpine valley of Switzerland.🇨🇭

With just ✌️more rounds to go in Snowshoe, 🇺🇸 can @myriam_nicole and @thibautdaprela hold on to their season lead and take the coveted overall WC title? 🏆

Stay tuned to the UCI MTB World Cup on Red Bull TV to find out. 📺 FULL REPLAY from Lenzerheide DH now available. 👀

#mtb #downhill #dh #mountainbike #lenzerheide #uci #ucimtbworldcup
